        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Knight Squad 2"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " contains a total of 13 game modes. Each mode is played with up to eight players and while you can play single-player with seven bots, the game is much more fun with as many friends you can get together. Each mode is uniquely different, ranging from Capture the Flag to Battle Royale to Soccer and each are worth at least one try until you and your friends decide on your favourites."
        ]
      ]
    ],
